avdta.project

Class TransitProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.project.Project
      • avdta.project.TransitProject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DemandProject

    public abstract class TransitProject
extends Project
    This is a project that contains transit vehicles. It adds a transit subfolder with transit data files.
